description: Main Stop Grill is a great food truck serving up a unique fusion of cuisines ranging from Caribbean to Southern, all with a Latin twist. The truck's specialties are its yuca bowls, each with its individual mojo sauce, and topped with grilled chicken breast w/garlic mojo, skirt steak w/chimichuri mojo, or shrimp w/lemon garlic mojo. Other offerings include battered gator bites, crab-stuffed shrimp, and much, much more. So stop by and check out the Main Stop Grill today!
name: Main Stop Grill
